Version 0.2.2:
- Update license to GPLv3 or later.

Version 0.2.1:
- Bug fixes.

Version 0.2.0:
- Multiple data sets in a single data file are now supported. The same viewing
  parameters are used for all data sets in a file. Opening a different file
  resets the parameters.
- The range selection widget allows to adjust the lower and upper bounds of the
  histogram. This allows much finer control over the selected range.

Version 0.1.2:
- Bug fixes.

Version 0.1.1:
- Bug fixes.

Version 0.1.0:
- Initial public release.
